a.n: FISH LIFE - A SEA OF LOVE

p.k: Submarine sexuality displays some very strange facets. Anything is possible underwater from behaviors close to ours to the most disturbing. There are those that move us because they live as a couple and never part. On the other end, some evolve in a transsexual harem: the females lead a tumultuous life governed by submissive/dominant relationships with the first female becoming the male when the latter dies... A world of astonishing and mysterious diversity.
